    <string name="timeline_how_to_play_text">Select gestures, animations and movements and add them to the line of actions. Once you have a combination that you like, press Play to put %1$s into action!</string>
    <string name="mouths_label">Draw the mouth</string>
    <string name="mouths_editor_label">Mouth editor</string>
    <string name="mouths_editor_how_to_play_text">With this editor, you can design your own mouth for Zowi. \nJust use your finger to draw one on your device.</string>
    <string name="mouths_how_to_play_text">Zowi\'s mouth will change. You need to draw Zowi\'s mouth on your device, in the least time possible. \nEach time you get it right, you\'ll go up one difficulty level. \nThe more you get right, the more points you\'ll win in order to the enter the ranking.</string>
