    <string name="how_to_play_title">How to play</string>
    <string name="zowi_says_how_to_play_text">%1$s will make a sequence of movements. Watch and remember them carefully! Then you have to repeat them by pressing the button with the picture that corresponds to each movement.\n\nIf you repeat the sequence correctly, %1$s will add another move. The more you get it right, the more points you will win to enter the ranking.</string>
